<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Medical Image Similarity Search</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Medical Image Similarity Search</h1>
            <p>Upload a medical image (e.g., X-rays or MRIs) and retrieve visually similar images from our database. This tool uses advanced AI models to provide fast and accurate image matching.</p>
        </header>
        <section>
            <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <input type="file" name="file" />
                <button type="submit">Upload Image</button>
            </form>
        </section>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Medical AI Solutions</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
